{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"盖被的人啊！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你应当起来，你应当警告，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你应当 颂扬你的主宰，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"你应当洗涤你的衣服，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你应当远离污 秽，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你不要施恩而求厚报，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"你应当为你的主而坚忍。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"当号角被吹响的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"在那时，将有一个艰难的 日子。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"那个日子对不信道者，是不容易渡过的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"你 让我独自处治我所创造的人吧！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"我曾赏赐他丰富的财 产，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"和在跟前的子嗣，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"我提高了他的声望，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"而他 还企望我再多加赏赐。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"绝不然！他确实是反对我的迹象 的，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"我将使他遭受苦难。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"他确已思考，确已计划。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"但无论他怎样计划， 他是被弃绝的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"无论他怎样计划，他终是被弃绝的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"他看一看，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"然后皱眉蹙额，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"然后高傲地转过身 去，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"而且说:“这只是传习的魔术，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"这只是凡人的言 辞。”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"我将使他堕入火狱，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"你怎能知道火狱是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"它不让任何物存在，不许任何物留下，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"它烧灼肌 435 肤。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"管理它的，共计十九名。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"我只将管理火狱的造 成天神，我只以他们的数目，考验不信道的人们，以便曾 受天经的人们认清，而信道的人们更加笃信;以免曾受天 经的人们和信道的人们怀疑;以便心中有病者和不信道者 说:“真主设这个譬喻做什么？”真主这样使他所意欲的人 误入迷途，使他所意欲的人遵循正路。只有你的主，能知 道他的军队，这只是人类的教训。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"真的，以月亮盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"以逝去时的黑夜盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"以 显照时的黎明盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"火狱确是一个大难，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"可以警告 人类，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"警告你们中欲前进的或欲后退的"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"各人将因自 己的营谋而作抵押，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"惟幸福的人们除外。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"他们在乐 园中互相询问，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"问犯罪人们的情状，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"“你们为什么 堕入火狱呢？”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"他们说:“我们没有礼拜，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"也没有济 贫，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"我们曾与妄言的人们同齐妄言，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"我们曾否认报 应日，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"一直到死亡降临我们。”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"说情者的说情，将 无益于他们。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"他们怎么退避这教训呢？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"他们好像一群惊慌的 驴子，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"刚逃避了一只狮子一样。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"不然，他们中的每 个人都希望获得一些展开的天经。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"绝不然，他们不畏 惧后世！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"真的，这确是一个教诲"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"谁愿意，谁记忆 它，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他们只因真主的意欲而记忆它。他是应受敬畏的， 他是宜于赦宥的。§ 436\t第七五章 复活（格雅迈）"}]}